    "ph_heading_text_Egf4wA": {
      "type": "ph-heading-text",
      "blocks": {
        "richtext_tKQfg3": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>PHORIA JEWELLERY LTD (“PHORIA”, “WE”, “OUR”, “US”)</p><p>PHORIA JEWELLERY LTD IS COMMITTED TO PROTECTING YOUR PRIVACY AND HANDLING YOUR PERSONAL INFORMATION LAWFULLY, FAIRLY AND TRANSPARENTLY.</p><p>THIS PRIVACY POLICY EXPLAINS HOW WE COLLECT, USE, STORE AND PROTECT YOUR PERSONAL DATA WHEN YOU BROWSE, PURCHASE FROM, OR OTHERWISE INTERACT WITH<a href=\"http://www.phoriajewellery.com\"> <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">WWW.PHORIAJEWELLERY.COM</span></a>.</p><p>WE COMPLY WITH:</p><ul><li>THE UK GENERAL DATA PROTECTION REGULATION (UK GDPR)</li><li>THE DATA PROTECTION ACT 2018</li><li>THE PRIVACY AND ELECTRONIC COMMUNICATIONS REGULATIONS (PECR)</li><li>CURRENT INFORMATION COMMISSIONER’S OFFICE (ICO) GUIDANCE (AS APPLICABLE IN 2026)</li></ul><p>IF YOU HAVE ANY QUESTIONS REGARDING THIS PRIVACY POLICY OR YOUR RIGHTS, PLEASE CONTACT US AT INFO@PHORIAJEWELLERY.COM</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "richtext_tKQfg3"
      ],
      "custom_css": [
        "@media screen and (max-width: 960px) {.ph-heading-text-section__title {padding-top: 20px; }}"
      ],
