    "ph_heading_text_mAV9Ck": {
      "type": "ph-heading-text",
      "blocks": {
        "richtext_EAE7tD": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>PHORIA JEWELLERY LTD</p><p>COMPANY NUMBER: 11951734</p><p>REGISTERED IN ENGLAND & WALES</p><p>EMAIL: INFO@PHORIAJEWELLERY.COM</p><p>PHORIA JEWELLERY LTD IS THE DATA CONTROLLER. THIS MEANS WE DETERMINE THE PURPOSES AND MEANS OF PROCESSING YOUR PERSONAL DATA.</p><p>WE ARE NOT LEGALLY REQUIRED TO APPOINT A DATA PROTECTION OFFICER. ALL DATA PROTECTION ENQUIRIES SHOULD BE DIRECTED TO THE EMAIL ADDRESS ABOVE.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "richtext_EAE7tD"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "title": "Who We Are",
        "bg_color": "#ffffff",
        "text_color": "#000000",
        "enable_animations": true
      }
    },
    "ph_heading_text_MkNdqY": {
      "type": "ph-heading-text",
      "blocks": {
        "richtext_ywUAiP": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>WE MAY COLLECT AND PROCESS THE FOLLOWING CATEGORIES OF PERSONAL DATA:</p><p>INFORMATION YOU PROVIDE</p><ul><li>FULL NAME</li><li>BILLING AND SHIPPING ADDRESS</li><li>EMAIL ADDRESS</li><li>PHONE NUMBER</li><li>PAYMENT METHOD DETAILS (PROCESSED SECURELY BY THIRD-PARTY PROVIDERS)</li><li>ACCOUNT DETAILS</li><li>MARKETING PREFERENCES</li><li>ORDER HISTORY</li><li>RETURNS AND WARRANTY INFORMATION</li></ul><p>AUTOMATICALLY COLLECTED INFORMATION</p><p>WHEN YOU VISIT OUR WEBSITE, WE MAY COLLECT:</p><ul><li>IP ADDRESS</li><li>DEVICE TYPE</li><li>BROWSER TYPE & VERSION</li><li>OPERATING SYSTEM</li><li>TIME ZONE</li><li>GENERAL LOCATION DATA</li><li>PAGES VISITED AND TIME SPENT</li><li>REFERRING URLS</li><li>COOKIE AND TRACKING DATA</li></ul><p>PAYMENT INFORMATION</p><p>PHORIA DOES NOT STORE FULL DEBIT OR CREDIT CARD DETAILS.</p><p>PAYMENTS ARE PROCESSED SECURELY BY:</p><ul><li>SHOPIFY PAYMENTS (STRIPE)</li><li>PAYPAL</li><li>KLARNA</li></ul><p>ALL PAYMENT PROVIDERS OPERATE AS INDEPENDENT DATA CONTROLLERS AND ARE REQUIRED TO BE GDPR-COMPLIANT.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "richtext_ywUAiP"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "title": "THE DATA WE COLLECT",
        "bg_color": "#ffffff",
        "text_color": "#000000",
        "enable_animations": true
      }
    },
    "ph_heading_text_4LwA8t": {
      "type": "ph-heading-text",
      "blocks": {
        "richtext_c3NVTa": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>WE USE YOUR PERSONAL DATA FOR THE FOLLOWING PURPOSES:</p><p>TO FULFIL YOUR ORDERS</p><ul><li>VERIFY PAYMENT</li><li>PROCESS TRANSACTIONS</li><li>DISPATCH GOODS</li><li>SEND ORDER CONFIRMATIONS</li><li>SEND SHIPPING UPDATES</li><li>HANDLE RETURNS, EXCHANGES AND WARRANTIES</li></ul><p>CUSTOMER SUPPORT</p><ul><li>RESPOND TO ENQUIRIES</li><li>PROVIDE ORDER UPDATES</li><li>RESOLVE ISSUES</li></ul><p>MARKETING (EMAIL & SMS)</p><p>WE ONLY SEND MARKETING COMMUNICATIONS WHERE:</p><ul><li>YOU HAVE PROVIDED CLEAR, INFORMED AND UNAMBIGUOUS CONSENT; OR</li><li>YOU QUALIFY FOR SOFT OPT-IN UNDER PECR (EXISTING CUSTOMER RELATIONSHIP AND CLEAR OPT-OUT PROVIDED)</li></ul><p>MARKETING MAY INCLUDE:</p><ul><li>PRODUCT ANNOUNCEMENTS</li><li>PROMOTIONS</li><li>DISCOUNTS</li><li>CART REMINDERS</li><li>BACK-IN-STOCK ALERTS</li><li>EXCLUSIVE OFFERS</li></ul><p>YOU MAY OPT OUT AT ANY TIME BY:</p><p>EMAIL: CLICKING “UNSUBSCRIBE”<br/>SMS: REPLYING “STOP”<br/>CONTACTING: INFO@PHORIAJEWELLERY.COM</p><p>OPT-OUT REQUESTS ARE PROCESSED WITHOUT UNDUE DELAY.</p><p>WEBSITE ANALYTICS & IMPROVEMENTS</p><p>WE USE ANALYTICS TO:</p><ul><li>IMPROVE WEBSITE PERFORMANCE</li><li>IDENTIFY TECHNICAL ISSUES</li><li>MONITOR TRAFFIC</li><li>PREVENT FRAUD</li></ul><p>LEGAL, COMPLIANCE & SECURITY</p><p>WE MAY PROCESS DATA TO:</p><ul><li>MEET TAX AND ACCOUNTING REQUIREMENTS</li><li>PREVENT FRAUD</li><li>MAINTAIN WEBSITE SECURITY</li><li>DEFEND LEGAL CLAIMS</li></ul>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "richtext_c3NVTa"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "title": "HOW WE USE YOUR INFORMATION",
        "bg_color": "#ffffff",
        "text_color": "#000000",
        "enable_animations": true
      }
    },
    "ph_heading_text_hejNXe": {
      "type": "ph-heading-text",
      "blocks": {
        "richtext_JrkaMc": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>UNDER UK GDPR, WE RELY ON:</p><p>CONTRACT</p><p>TO PROCESS AND FULFIL YOUR ORDERS.</p><p>CONSENT</p><p>FOR:</p><ul><li>EMAIL MARKETING</li><li>SMS MARKETING</li><li>NON-ESSENTIAL COOKIES</li><li>CERTAIN ANALYTICS</li></ul><p>YOU MAY WITHDRAW CONSENT AT ANY TIME.</p><p>LEGITIMATE INTERESTS</p><p>FOR:</p><ul><li>WEBSITE SECURITY</li><li>FRAUD PREVENTION</li><li>SYSTEM MONITORING</li><li>MAINTAINING SUPPRESSION LISTS</li></ul><p>WE DO NOT RELY ON LEGITIMATE INTEREST FOR UNSOLICITED SMS OR EMAIL MARKETING.</p><p>LEGAL OBLIGATION</p><p>FOR:</p><ul><li>TAX RECORD-KEEPING</li><li>ACCOUNTING</li><li>REGULATORY COMPLIANCE</li></ul>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "richtext_JrkaMc"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "title": "LEGAL BASIS FOR PROCESSING",
        "bg_color": "#ffffff",
        "text_color": "#000000",
        "enable_animations": true
      }
    },
    "ph_heading_text_GURzPV": {
      "type": "ph-heading-text",
      "blocks": {
        "richtext_jCfD3c": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>WE SHARE YOUR DATA ONLY WHERE NECESSARY AND WITH TRUSTED SERVICE PROVIDERS:</p><p>E-COMMERCE & OPERATIONS</p><ul><li>SHOPIFY</li><li>PAYMENT PROVIDERS (STRIPE, PAYPAL, KLARNA)</li><li>SMS PROVIDERS</li><li>EMAIL MARKETING PLATFORMS</li><li>DELIVERY COURIERS</li></ul><p>ANALYTICS & ADVERTISING</p><ul><li>GOOGLE ANALYTICS</li><li>META (WHERE USED)</li><li>SHOPIFY ANALYTICS</li></ul><p>SERVICE PROVIDERS</p><ul><li>CUSTOMER SUPPORT TOOLS</li><li>REVIEW PLATFORMS</li><li>FRAUD PREVENTION SERVICES</li></ul><p>ALL THIRD PARTIES PROCESS DATA UNDER CONTRACTUAL DATA PROCESSING AGREEMENTS.</p><p>WE DO NOT SELL PERSONAL DATA.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "richtext_jCfD3c"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "title": "SHARING YOUR DATA",
        "bg_color": "#ffffff",
        "text_color": "#000000",
        "enable_animations": true
      }
    },
    "ph_heading_text_wX7Y6m": {
      "type": "ph-heading-text",
      "blocks": {
        "richtext_6QWrGQ": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>SOME PROVIDERS MAY PROCESS DATA OUTSIDE THE UK.</p><p>WHERE THIS OCCURS, WE IMPLEMENT SAFEGUARDS SUCH AS:</p><ul><li>UK INTERNATIONAL DATA TRANSFER AGREEMENTS (IDTAS)</li><li>UK ADDENDUM TO EU STANDARD CONTRACTUAL CLAUSES</li><li>ADEQUACY DECISIONS</li></ul>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "richtext_6QWrGQ"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "title": "INTERNATIONAL DATA TRANSFERS",
        "bg_color": "#ffffff",
        "text_color": "#000000",
        "enable_animations": true
      }
