        "richtext_M9WWAW": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>LAST UPDATED: JANUARY 2026</p><p>THIS SECTION EXPLAINS HOW PHORIA JEWELLERY LTD COLLECTS AND PROCESSES PERSONAL DATA FOR OUR SMS MARKETING SERVICE.</p><p>WE COLLECT:</p><ul><li>TELEPHONE NUMBER</li><li>COUNTRY INFORMATION</li><li>CONSENT RECORDS (DATE, TIME, METHOD, WORDING DISPLAYED)</li><li>DELIVERY STATUS AND OPT-OUT LOGS</li></ul><p>WE USE YOUR DATA TO:</p><ul><li>SEND SMS MARKETING (WITH VALID CONSENT OR SOFT OPT-IN)</li><li>PROCESS OPT-OUT REQUESTS</li><li>MAINTAIN SUPPRESSION LISTS</li><li>COMPLY WITH PECR AND UK GDPR</li></ul><p>LEGAL BASIS:</p><p>CONSENT (ARTICLE 6(1)(A) UK GDPR)<br/>SOFT OPT-IN UNDER PECR (WHERE APPLICABLE)</p><p>WE DO NOT SEND SMS WITHOUT A VALID LEGAL BASIS.</p><p>WE SHARE SMS DATA ONLY WITH GDPR-COMPLIANT SMS PROCESSORS UNDER CONTRACT.</p><p>RETENTION:</p><p>CONSENT RECORDS: UP TO 6 YEARS<br/>SUPPRESSION LISTS: RETAINED FOR COMPLIANCE<br/>TECHNICAL LOGS: UP TO 12 MONTHS</p><p>YOU MAY WITHDRAW CONSENT AT ANY TIME BY TEXTING STOP OR EMAILING US.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
